  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 180&deg;C/ 160&deg;C (fan)/ 350&deg;F/ Gas 4</p>\r\n<p>Boil kettle&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Cut the <strong>waxy&nbsp;potatoes</strong>&nbsp;(skins on) into bite-sized pieces&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>potatoes</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 15 min or until fork-tender</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/885.-step1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/885.-step1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/885.-step1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/885.-step1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/885.-step1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top, tail and peel the <strong>carrot</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"><strong>[s]</strong></span>, then continue to peel lengths until you end up with a pile of '<strong>carrot</strong>&nbsp;<strong>ribbons</strong>'&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Trim then peel the <strong>cucumber</strong>&nbsp;into ribbons, discarding the seedy core</p>\r\n<p>Squeeze any excess liquid out of the '<strong>cucumber</strong> <strong>ribbons</strong>'</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/885.-step2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/885.-step2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/885.-step2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/885.-step2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/885.-step2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>mango chutney</strong> with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> in a large bowl&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Add 3/4 of the <strong>nigella seeds</strong> and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>carrot</strong> and <strong>cucumber</strong>&nbsp;<strong>ribbons</strong> to the bowl and mix well - this is your <strong>Indian&nbsp;slaw</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/885.-step3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/885.-step3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/885.-step3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/885.-step3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/885.-step3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drizzle the <strong>ciabatta rolls</strong> with a little <strong>olive oil</strong> and sprinkle over the remaining <strong>nigella seeds</strong></p>\r\n<p>Add them to a baking tray and put it in the oven for 5 min or until they are crispy and golden</p>\r\n<p>Once crispy, remove from the oven and set aside to cool</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/885.-step4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/885.-step4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/885.-step4-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/885.-step4-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/885.-step4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut the <strong>paneer</strong> in half so you have two '<strong>steaks</strong>'</p>\r\n<p>Pat the <strong>paneer</strong> <strong>steaks</strong>&nbsp;dry with kitchen paper</p>\r\n<p>Rub them with a little <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and season both sides with the<strong> garam masala</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/885.-step5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/885.-step5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/885.-step5-x700.jpg",
