          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/885.-step5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong>, over a medium heat&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>paneer steaks</strong> and cook for 2-3 min on each side until they are brown and crispy</p>",
